'''Azizbek Amonov''' ([[Cyrillic alphabets#Uzbek|Uzbek Cyrillic]]: Азизбек Аскарович Аманов; born 30 October 1997) is an Uzbek [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[FC Bukhara|Buxoro]] and the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].<ref>[https://fbref.com/en/players/f487314f/Azizbek-Amonov Azizbek Amonov]</ref><ref>[https://www.fotmob.com/players/933051/azizbek-amonov AZIZBEK AMONOV]</ref><ref>[https://www.eurosport.com/football/azizbek-amonov_prs504115/person.shtml Azizbek Amonov]</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tarafdari.com/node/2071757|title=عزیزبک آمانوف به استقلال پیوست / رسمی|website=www.tarafdari.com|date=4 February 2022 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://footballi.net/news/r/697353/%D9%87%D8%A7%D9%81%D8%A8%DA%A9-%D8%A7%D8%B2%D8%A8%DA%A9-%D8%B1%D8%B3%D9%85%D8%A7-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D9%82%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%84-%D9%BE%DB%8C%D9%88%D8%B3%D8%AA|title=هافبک ازبک رسما به استقلال پیوست|website=footballi.net|date=4 February 2022 }}</ref>

==Club career==
===Bunyodkor===
Azizbek signed a contract with Bunyodkor on 10 January 2025.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://championat.asia/uz/news/terma-jamoamiz-azosi-faoliyatini-bunyodkorda-davom-ettiradi|title=Терма жамоамиз аъзоси фаолиятини "Бунёдкор"да давом эттиради|website=championat.asia|date=10 January 2025 }}</ref>

